# AnyRegexOutput.Element

**Structure**

An individual match output value.

## Declaration

```swift
struct Element
```

## Instance Properties

- **name**: The name of this capture, if the capture is named.
- **range**: The range over which a value was captured, if there was a capture.
- **substring**: The slice of the input which was captured, if there was a capture.
- **type**: The type of this capture.
- **value**: The captured value, if there was a capture.
